{
  "uid": "champy-api-performance",
  "title": "Champy - API Performance",
  "description": "Performance de l'API d'inférence : latences, débit, erreurs et endpoints les plus sollicités.",
  "tags": [
    "api",
    "champy",
    "performance"
  ],
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 3,
  "editable": true,
  "refresh": "15s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-1h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "timezone": "browser",
  "templating": {
    "list": []
  },
  "annotations": {
    "list": []
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "À propos de ce tableau de bord",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**Performance de l'API d'inférence Champy.** Ce tableau de bord suit la rapidité et le volume des prédictions servies par l'API BentoML. Les latences proviennent des métriques métier `champy_prediction_*`, le trafic des métriques natives `bentoml_service_request_total`. Les endpoints de healthcheck (`/health`, `/healthz`) sont exclus des vues de trafic pour ne montrer que l'activité réelle.\n\n**Contenu :**\n- **Latence d'inférence (p50/p95/p99)** : temps de réponse aux percentiles clés ; le p99 révèle les pires cas.\n- **Latence moyenne (5 min)** : latence moyenne récente, repère rapide.\n- **Total prédictions** : nombre cumulé de prédictions depuis le démarrage de l'API.\n- **Requêtes par seconde (par endpoint)** : débit de trafic métier par route.\n- **Erreurs HTTP (par endpoint)** : taux de réponses non-2xx ; vide = aucune erreur (état nominal).\n- **Top endpoints (par volume)** : routes les plus sollicitées (hors healthchecks)."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Latence d'inférence (p50 / p95 / p99)",
      "description": "Temps de réponse de l'inférence de bout-en-bout (preprocessing + ONNX) aux percentiles 50, 95 et 99, calculé sur 5 min.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 16,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 6
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum(rate(champy_prediction_latency_seconds_bucket[5m])) by (le))",
          "legendFormat": "p50",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(champy_prediction_latency_seconds_bucket[5m])) by (le))",
          "legendFormat": "p95",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum(rate(champy_prediction_latency_seconds_bucket[5m])) by (le))",
          "legendFormat": "p99",
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": true
          },
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Latence moyenne (5 min)",
      "description": "Latence moyenne des prédictions sur les 5 dernières minutes.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 16,
        "y": 6
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "rate(champy_prediction_latency_seconds_sum[5m]) / rate(champy_prediction_latency_seconds_count[5m])",
          "legendFormat": "Latence moyenne (5 min)",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "blue",
                "value": null
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "textMode": "value"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Total prédictions (depuis démarrage)",
      "description": "Nombre cumulé de prédictions servies depuis le dernier démarrage de l'API (compteur, remis à zéro au redéploiement).",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 16,
        "y": 10
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum(champy_predictions_total)",
          "legendFormat": "Total predictions (depuis demarrage)",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "blue",
                "value": null
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "textMode": "value"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Requêtes par seconde (par endpoint)",
      "description": "Débit de requêtes par route métier (healthchecks exclus), calculé sur 1 min.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 14
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum(rate(bentoml_service_request_total{endpoint!~\"/health.*\"}[1m])) by (endpoint)",
          "legendFormat": "{{endpoint}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": true
          },
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Erreurs HTTP (par endpoint)",
      "description": "Taux de réponses non-2xx par endpoint. Un graphe vide signifie aucune erreur (état nominal).",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 14
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum(rate(bentoml_service_request_total{http_response_code!~\"2..\"}[5m])) by (endpoint, http_response_code)",
          "legendFormat": "{{endpoint}} {{http_response_code}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": true
          },
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Top endpoints (par volume cumulé)",
      "description": "Routes les plus sollicitées depuis le démarrage (healthchecks exclus), triées par nombre total de requêtes.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 22
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "topk(5, sum by (endpoint) (bentoml_service_request_total{endpoint!~\"/health.*\"}))",
          "legendFormat": "",
          "refId": "A",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": {
              "Time": true,
              "__name__": true,
              "job": true,
              "instance": true,
              "service": true
            },
            "renameByName": {
              "endpoint": "Endpoint",
              "Value": "Requetes (cumul)"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "sortBy",
          "options": {
            "sort": [
              {
                "field": "Requetes (cumul)",
                "desc": true
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {},
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "showHeader": true
      }
    }
  ]
}
